Package: LTRtrace
Type: Package
Title: Tracing LTR Retrotransposons by Integrating Intact LTR-RT Annotation,
    Reusable LTR Library Construction, Taxonomic Classification, and
    Automated SoloLTR Detection
Version: 1.1.0
Date: 2026-06-25
Authors@R: c(
    person("User", "Liurxx", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "liurxx@example.com"))
Description: LTRtrace was designed to trace LTR retrotransposons by integrating
    intact LTR-RT annotation, reusable LTR library construction, taxonomic
    classification, and automated SoloLTR detection. Starting from a genome
    FASTA file and centromere BED file, the pipeline runs LTR_FINDER,
    LTR_HARVEST, LTR_retriever, TEsorter, CD-HIT, and BLAST to produce
    comprehensive soloLTR classification, deep annotation of CEN/Peri-CEN
    regions, FASTA sequence extraction, and publication-ready stacked bar
    plots of LTR family composition.
